short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension that enhances GitHub by displaying full dates and detailed contributor information

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This project is a Chrome extension named GitHub Enhancer. It enhances the GitHub browsing experience by displaying full dates and detailed contributor information. The extension uses content scripts to inject JavaScript and CSS into GitHub pages, providing features like enhanced contributor cards and customizable settings.
